    "description": "<strong>Love Exalt 8372</strong> is a mystery visual novel inspired by games like <strong>Danganronpa,</strong> <strong>Your Turn to Die,</strong> and the <strong>Zero Escape</strong> series.<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2295280/extras/67e624a6e6f83a29c051be8b9cc31a17.avif?t=1765396040\" width=596 height=414 /></span><br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2295280/extras/98d1c5981621875f1132d9580826b7b9.avif?t=1765396040\" width=596 height=82 /></span><br><br>In a world where monsters have been farmed to extinction for XP, <strong>twelve people</strong> with unique <strong>RPG class types</strong> board a train; among these twelve people, the <strong>last monster</strong> is hiding. Some passengers are oblivious victims... while others boarded this train with a plan <strong>already in motion.</strong><br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2295280/extras/1f8f85bf461c437c1bc5875fbabf5fa1.avif?t=1765396040\" width=608 height=1815 /></span><br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2295280/extras/58037ef2635883a991639aa3182cb3c6.avif?t=1765396040\" width=596 height=82 /></span><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2295280/extras/a889bd5b6c0415fd71807e17bf544dd5.poster.avif?t=1765396040\" width=596 height=334 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2295280/extras/a889bd5b6c0415fd71807e17bf544dd5.webm?t=1765396040\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2295280/extras/a889bd5b6c0415fd71807e17bf544dd5.mp4?t=1765396040\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2295280/extras/fdfea3aac3d81313aa0a932a178e15f2.avif?t=1765396040\" width=596 height=82 /></span><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline crossorigin=\"anonymous\" poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2295280/extras/1d085dd274df70a3b64bb217e1860e69.poster.avif?t=1765396040\" width=596 height=335 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2295280/extras/1d085dd274df70a3b64bb217e1860e69.webm?t=1765396040\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"></video></span><br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2295280/extras/fe41791a7dc9d5084a9ff3d84193e044.avif?t=1765396040\" width=596 height=82 /></span><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2295280/extras/483f9125744046c4450cfc5bc2732815.poster.avif?t=1765396040\" width=596 height=334 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2295280/extras/483f9125744046c4450cfc5bc2732815.webm?t=1765396040\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2295280/extras/483f9125744046c4450cfc5bc2732815.mp4?t=1765396040\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2295280/extras/f1780545272d03d99d3f40fb759ec0a3.avif?t=1765396040\" width=596 height=82 /></span><br><br><strong>Act 1</strong> is complete, and <strong>Act 2</strong> is underway. New updates will add chapters to the story, new minigames, animations, art, music, and polish for the rest of the existing game. Join our Discord to discuss the developments!<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><picture><source srcset=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2295280/extras/bbbb310bbdf9aeddaed78d974928bedc.apng?t=1765396040\"><img src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2295280/extras/bbbb310bbdf9aeddaed78d974928bedc.poster.avif?t=1765396040\" class=\"bb_img\" width=596 height=118 /></picture></span><br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2295280/extras/df2240db10604fd78001d149915f7813.avif?t=1765396040\" width=596 height=82 /></span><br><br>There is a demo! It includes the first scene, <strong>Act 1 Scene 1: Last Call.</strong> If you decide to buy the game afterwards, all your game progress will be transferred to the full version, including steam achievements!<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2295280/extras/b76473e651eadb27a30ba970cc57bfcc.avif?t=1765396040\" width=293 height=178 /></span>",
